\c 117 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 117\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Sabni Hundinuu Waaqayyoon Jajachuu
\m \bd 1\bd* Namoonni lafa irraa hundinuu Waaqayyoon jajadhaa! Sabni hundinuu isa faarfadhaa.
\m \bd 2\bd* Gaarummaan inni nuuf qabu guddaa jabaa dha, amanamummaan isaas bara baraan in jiraata. Waaqayyoon jajadhaa!
\b 
